  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/5847ce0914f7246ea4eb4167746761dc.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/5847ce0914f7246ea4eb4167746761dc.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/5847ce0914f7246ea4eb4167746761dc.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/1bb4d7c20bed51121d1b0ae76c869e55.webp?t=1735247300\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Hung, an adventurous risk-taker with an insatiable hunger for extraordinary experiences, seeks out a cheap and creepy house for a thrilling one-day rental. Little does he know that the house has a dark history, with a young girl's murder nearby. Ignoring the warnings, Hung decides to stay, and soon finds himself in the midst of a terrifying nightmare. He encounters the ghost of the murdered girl, setting off a series of haunting trials and challenges. Trapped and hunted in the haunted house, Hung must solve puzzles and face unimaginable horrors in a desperate attempt to escape. The chilling ghost story unravels as Hung's life hangs in the balance, leaving him forever scarred by the terrifying ordeal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/d0d3e16f4a3919c63bf85a4c6f56c657.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/d0d3e16f4a3919c63bf85a4c6f56c657.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/d0d3e16f4a3919c63bf85a4c6f56c657.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/201d728942e7a48b389c6da7389237df.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/201d728942e7a48b389c6da7389237df.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/201d728942e7a48b389c6da7389237df.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/634f8258beab00fe41b5d406d5b9c4f0.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/634f8258beab00fe41b5d406d5b9c4f0.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/634f8258beab00fe41b5d406d5b9c4f0.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/fdda8c12ceb069e3710546bd7d5b7de3.webp?t=1735247300\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Prepare yourself for a bone-chilling adventure in \"Stay Still 2,\" the thrilling ghost story that will keep you on the edge of your seat! Hung, a risk-taking adventurer, seeks out the most extraordinary experiences. When he stumbles upon a cheap, creepy house with a dark history, he can't resist the temptation to stay for a night filled with spine-tingling thrills.<br><br>Explore the eerie house and uncover its haunting past as you encounter mysterious figures and disturbing noises. Piece together clues and solve terrifying puzzles in a desperate attempt to escape the clutches of the vengeful ghost. But beware, the horrors within are beyond imagination!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/315cfd43ba8c926b5830da55d2a0a5ec.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/315cfd43ba8c926b5830da55d2a0a5ec.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/315cfd43ba8c926b5830da55d2a0a5ec.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/f4e460d274e6b50143721b5f418fa76a.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/f4e460d274e6b50143721b5f418fa76a.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/f4e460d274e6b50143721b5f418fa76a.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/943531c537621d811bc5202a1b3e734d.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/943531c537621d811bc5202a1b3e734d.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/943531c537621d811bc5202a1b3e734d.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/87e20e4ff6bee79feb57f7f45e3d73c4.webp?t=1735247300\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in a chilling ghost story filled with suspense and mystery.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Navigate through the dark and eerie house to confront the ghost's tragic past.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve diabolical puzzles and riddles to find the key to your survival.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience heart-pounding moments and a sense of dread that will stay with you long after the game ends.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/4257fb685a89f74b90ce6ddeb23f02fd.poster.avif?t=1735247300\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/4257fb685a89f74b90ce6ddeb23f02fd.webm?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537770/extras/4257fb685a89f74b90ce6ddeb23f02fd.mp4?t=1735247300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
